Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.46,0:00:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 我到底还能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.31,0:00:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了改变那如狭隘庭园般的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还活不到人生的一半
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.26,0:00:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反抗 相拥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在无意识中被刻上的经验纹身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.30,0:00:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当站在悬崖边的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.47,0:00:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦难抓住了我的手腕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次看到了自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.08,0:00:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往更加宽广的领域\N往更深更大的某处
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.19,0:01:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝着无法预测的世界前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.13,0:01:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And lt's calling me again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.96,0:01:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空中城市目视确认
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.26,0:01:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,规模不断扩展，似乎要覆盖住夏威夷上空了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.85,0:01:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些突然出现在空中的城市群
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.47,0:01:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断扩展就像是要包裹住整个地球一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.77,0:01:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前仍在不断增殖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.64,0:01:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然地球联合认为这些城市群为战斗性武器的可能性极低
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.27,0:01:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且发表了希望民众遵守正常社会秩序的声明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.44,0:02:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是伦敦、德黑兰、上海等17座城市已经发生了暴动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.74,0:02:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后的事态…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.85,0:02:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.44,0:02:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么长时间不在，真是很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.57,0:02:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，大家都期待着司令官的归来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.15,0:02:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.36,0:02:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么今天看起来这么有精神啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.16,0:02:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.74,0:02:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，大家少废话了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.16,0:02:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作，工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.66,0:02:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正面临关键性的局面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.66,0:02:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.04,0:02:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫东大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.25,0:02:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.38,0:02:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次，我打算和神名一起吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.34,0:02:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.44,0:03:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.36,0:03:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目击情报称仅关西地区就超过了80个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.16,0:03:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“其中，MU族28个，构造物30…”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.86,0:03:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界开始重合了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.87,0:03:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.96,0:03:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也…？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.54,0:03:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.84,0:03:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在综合衍射图上显示的这个自称是MU族特使的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.68,0:03:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经确认为前国防部一佐——九鬼正义
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MU大战爆发后不久就行踪不明了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.47,0:03:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据后来的调查
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.64,0:03:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怀疑他潜伏在绝对障壁内
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.85,0:03:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将我们从时间的牢狱中解放出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.36,0:04:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对此我要对给予我们帮助的诸位表示感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.36,0:04:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外，我命令诸位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.16,0:04:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即解除武装并且交出Xephon
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.66,0:04:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给你们24小时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.25,0:04:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果拒绝以上要求…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.25,0:04:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸位难免大难临头
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.17,0:04:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是30分钟前，摧毁中京地区的D-1影像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.17,0:04:23.34,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}中京：名古屋的别称，相对于东京（江户）、西京（京都）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.26,0:04:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个D-1的全长推测为2.6公里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.85,0:04:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,质量为10的9次方吨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.27,0:04:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的破坏力为…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.65,0:04:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10的27次方尔格(erg)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.65,0:04:37.94,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}尔格(erg)：能量单位，1尔格相当于10的负7次方焦耳(J)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.57,0:04:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么恐怖的东西要来这里啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.57,0:04:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题是包裹着RahXephon的这个卵形构造物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.66,0:04:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就所有的物理性接近方式对它都不奏效这点来看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.37,0:04:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它可能是一种不同的维度空间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.37,0:04:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在别说是启动RahXephon了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.66,0:04:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是搬运它也很困难
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗力上的差距十分明显啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.75,0:05:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要怎么办啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.17,0:05:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然要战斗到底！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.84,0:05:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为，我们是TERRA
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法接受！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.06,0:05:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为副司令我有权对\N这种鲁莽的作战计划提出反对意见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.44,0:05:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧，少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.78,0:05:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是不会回心转意的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.94,0:05:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一点你最清楚吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.57,0:05:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,树！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.07,0:05:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是个不得要领的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.24,0:05:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此以外，别无它法…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.37,0:05:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对此我很羡慕…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.04,0:05:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你稍微替她想想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.88,0:05:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个和这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会保护她的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.55,0:05:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就去保护吧，少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.97,0:05:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经想保护的就没能…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.44,0:06:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狡猾…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真狡猾…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.65,0:06:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功刀先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狡猾！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.04,0:06:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离最后一班船出港还有1小时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还留在此处的市民
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请按指定路线，立即到港口去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.55,0:06:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离最后一班船出港还有1小时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.47,0:06:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要这样做？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.56,0:06:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是扎在我记忆中的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.06,0:06:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一根像刺一样的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天必须要拔掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.94,0:06:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.57,0:06:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能邀请我来TERRA…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.36,0:06:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.68,0:07:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他兴奋过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.26,0:07:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不是我而是他？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.76,0:07:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是你的任务吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.14,0:07:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是olin的守护者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.27,0:08:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是yólteótl的见证者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…麻弥大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.06,0:08:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在做的事情真的是正确的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.07,0:08:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样真正的正确的世界真的会来临吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三轮，没有什么可担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.16,0:08:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.54,0:08:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做的事是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.35,0:08:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五味~呀~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.14,0:08:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的明天在哪里啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.98,0:08:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别问我！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.44,0:08:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了对岸，会让我们下船是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.57,0:08:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，这艘船有它自己的船员呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.24,0:08:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，你和八云君谈过了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:08:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要好好谈谈啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.87,0:09:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.64,0:09:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是个好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，是个好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.48,0:09:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管发生了很多事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.06,0:09:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟那里曾经是我的家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次感到失去什么了…吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.74,0:09:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.66,0:09:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你身边，默默注视着你的人，去在意她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.17,0:09:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一直，只想着你一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.26,0:09:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.55,0:09:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是个好女人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.36,0:10:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-1确定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.87,0:10:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到达第一级防卫线还有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.37,0:10:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10秒±20…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.78,0:10:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八云司令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.74,0:11:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻象系统已经进入迎击位置
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.24,0:11:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事？少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.54,0:11:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你从这里发布指挥命令吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.17,0:11:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.04,0:11:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那，是谁？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.96,0:11:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻象系统发射
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前正向D-1的航线飞去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航线修正，与敌人相遇还有20秒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.14,0:11:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是老样子，卖命工作的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.48,0:11:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…17区，侵入蓝色位置
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旋风导弹迎击发射准备
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.75,0:11:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻象4号，消失
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.87,0:11:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第4小队区支援第7区
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.54,0:11:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第1到第4区
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.25,0:11:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.05,0:12:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻象4号，消失
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.05,0:12:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第7区的防御体制…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.18,0:12:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算是老友重逢了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.14,0:12:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功刀一尉？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.14,0:12:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，现在是TERRA的司令官大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.57,0:12:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残存战斗力到60区集结
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指令确认
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.07,0:12:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到部下变得优秀了的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.24,0:12:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为上司，没有比这更令我开心的了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Delta阵型
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.25,0:12:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布奇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.67,0:12:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.26,0:12:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.56,0:12:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不还给我吗？那只猫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.56,0:12:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:12:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想听
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:12:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.36,0:13:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.78,0:13:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.17,0:13:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个身影…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.67,0:13:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…果然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.75,0:13:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旋风导弹的火力集中到D-1的下部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.34,0:13:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指令确认
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.76,0:13:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了现在你还敢顶撞我？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.64,0:13:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.06,0:13:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过，这就叫“把别人的好心当成歹意” …
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当初下命令的是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.14,0:13:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过，直接执行的人，却是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.65,0:13:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的这双手杀死了你女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.15,0:13:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全弹齐射！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.17,0:13:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用没用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.75,0:14:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的，功刀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.64,0:14:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.06,0:14:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是被称为MU族的人们为了送走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.64,0:14:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与Xephon接触的奏者而使用的通路…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏者？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.65,0:14:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是olin
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.36,0:14:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原先的olin们都从这里通过…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.15,0:14:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.45,0:14:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊修特利
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.16,0:14:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Xephon的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷失的olin如果在具有资格的年龄——17岁时找到我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.37,0:14:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那“真实”的“容颜”被认识为伊修特利(ixtli)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.67,0:14:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,olin成为“真实”的“心脏”——yólteótl进行调律
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.17,0:14:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调律什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.55,0:14:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.97,0:14:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并没有希望你这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.27,0:14:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这不可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.27,0:14:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.44,0:15:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第3区被毁灭、第14区被毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.36,0:15:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第17区被毁灭…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.38,0:15:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果调律没有完成就结束了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.96,0:15:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界就会变回成“泥之海”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.05,0:15:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是“真实”的“容颜”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.97,0:15:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不希望我存在，就无法…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.28,0:16:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别勉强了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经干的很不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了，无聊的余兴节目结束了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,余兴节目现在刚刚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一佐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.94,0:17:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jupiter系统启动…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.37,0:17:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？ ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.75,0:17:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.66,0:17:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不会吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.34,0:17:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没听说过有这种东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.34,0:17:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功刀！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.68,0:18:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jupiter现象…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根来彼方几乎全部被覆盖了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真理子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.25,0:18:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.46,0:18:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.84,0:18:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.97,0:19:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道…可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jupiter现象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.28,0:19:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.57,0:19:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你思念的人，恐怕就在那里面…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.24,0:19:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.75,0:19:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.17,0:19:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望我存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…看起来好像害怕着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.84,0:19:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我害怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.05,0:19:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来就像人类一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.64,0:19:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.06,0:19:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.77,0:19:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，我害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.06,0:19:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总在我身边，保护着我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.28,0:20:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在，我有想去保护的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.36,0:20:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直没有意识到…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.74,0:20:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,olin
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.95,0:20:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是绫人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.97,0:20:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你一起活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.05,0:20:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起保护她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.55,0:20:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.27,0:20:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.98,0:20:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.94,0:20:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神由根源之地驾临的岛，根来岛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.15,0:20:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美丽的岛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.45,0:20:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫人他？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.24,0:20:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.45,0:20:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.45,0:20:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到你的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.16,0:20:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.04,0:20:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.67,0:21:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.76,0:21:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.44,0:21:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的曲子是为谁弹的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.07,0:21:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.28,0:21:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向他告别…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.57,0:21:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.07,0:21:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是和你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.05,0:21:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就要回来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.18,0:21:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.85,0:23:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你，根据重叠的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.65,0:23:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道那个理由
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.57,0:23:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.15,0:23:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集，第二十四乐章
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.74,0:23:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通往调律的门
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.74,0:23:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界饱含着声音